<h4>2. Rate estimation</h4>
<blockquote>
<input type="button" name="ESTIMATE" value="Estimate an instantaneous Rate" onClick="EstimateRate();" />
with the EM method and the Kalman filter.
<BR>
<applet code="SulabApplet1.class" name="SulabApplet1" width="550" height="280">
</applet>
<BR>
<input type="button" name="ESTIMATE" value="Estimate more accurately" onClick="EstimateAccurately();" />
with the non-Gaussian filter in place of the Kalman filter.<BR>
<em>This process takes a bit more time.</em>
<BR>
</blockquote>

<h4>3. Output sheet</h4>
<blockquote>
<input type="button" name="DATASHEETKALMAN" value="Output Data Sheet" onClick="DataSheetKalman();" />
of the instantaneous Rate estimated with the Kalman filter.<BR>
<em>Estimation is carried out at every inter-event interval.</em>
<BR>
<BR>
<input type="button" name="DATASHEETNONGAUSSIAN" value="Output Data Sheet" onClick="DataSheetNonGaussian();" />
of the instantaneous Rate estimated with the non-Gaussian filter.<BR>
